From 9ec3d92046c1f7d3b8ccbe4bdbd2dda2b3f76bf3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Simon W. Jackson" <simon@simonwjackson.io>
Date: Sat, 23 May 2026 03:31:53 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add v4l2m2m platform: iris VPU decode with SDL NV12
 presentation

